longBusinessSummary: Quinsam Capital Corporation operates as a investment and merchant banking firm in Canada. It primarily focuses on investment in technology, healthcare, mining and exploration, e-sports, and cannabis markets. The company's activities include acquisitions, advisory services, lending activities, and portfolio investments. Quinsam Capital Corporation was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
